=================================
    Communication Master Node
=================================

This ROS package provides communication nodes for publishing/subscribing and
running services within a distributed multiple-robot system.

It provides the following nodes:
    1) request_robot_status: requests status updates from all robots in the system
    2) communication_master: publishes status updates to all robots in the system


===== DEPENDENCIES =====

ROS Electric
formation_control (ROS package)



===== USE WITH THESE ROS PACKAGES =====

hive_master
formation_control



===== INSTALLATION =====

1) Move the source of this package ot the ROS workspace folder

2) From inside the package, run rosmake.
   - If rosmake fails,
     - check that the required packages are installed
     - check the CMakeCache.txt file in the build folder. If it exists,
       remove it and run rosmake again.



===== HOW TO LAUNCH =====

1) If not already running, launch roscore
2) Run the command:



